text: "Greetings, this is NAMESLOTA with Amazon Customer service. "
It seems that our computer system charged you three times for your last order.
I don't recall seeing 3 transactions on my account.
"There was recently a glitch with our billing software, we are trying to stop it."
So will you be refunding the money through the account info you have on file?
"Yes, but the billing department needs some information from you."
It seems we lost some data.
What kind of information do you need?
First I need your full name and billing address.
Is that the reason my heater has not com yet?
"I can look that up for you, but I need your full name and billing address first."
How did you get my phone number if you lost my contact information?
"We need this information for verification purposes, just a formality."
Are you going to need my credit card information for this?
